    <item>
      <title>Bypass Me writeup</title>
      <link>https://www.zhienw.com/post/bypass_me/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 11:30:52 &#43;0800</pubDate>
      <author>ray784523@zhienw.com (Zhi Chen)</author>
      <guid>https://www.zhienw.com/post/bypass_me/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>Bypass Me writeup</h1><p>作者：Zhi Chen（ray784523@zhienw.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="獲取與查看題目">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%8d%b2%e5%8f%96%e8%88%87%e6%9f%a5%e7%9c%8b%e9%a1%8c%e7%9b%ae"></a>
獲取與查看題目
</h2><p><strong>連接題目主機</strong></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-SHELL" data-lang="SHELL"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">#題目提供連線方法</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ssh ctf-player@foggy-cliff.picoctf.net -p <span class="m">56563</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ls
</span></span></code></pre></div><p><img src="/images/Bypass_me/1.webp" alt="image">
<strong>查看題目</strong></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">file bypassme.bin
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">./bypassme.bin
</span></span></code></pre></div><p><img src="/images/Bypass_me/2.webp" alt="image">
<strong>下載題目用做後續分析</strong></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">scp -P 56563 ctf-player@foggy-cliff.picoctf.net:bypassme.bin ./
</span></span></code></pre></div><p><img src="/images/Bypass_me/3.webp" alt="image"></p>
<h2 id="使用-ida-進行靜態分析">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8-ida-%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c%e9%9d%9c%e6%85%8b%e5%88%86%e6%9e%90"></a>
使用 IDA 進行靜態分析
</h2><p><strong>點選 yes</strong>
<img src="/images/Bypass_me/4.webp" alt="image">
<strong>程式選擇密碼儲存位置,並發現有一個函數_Z15decode_passwordPc</strong>
<img src="/images/Bypass_me/5.webp" alt="image">
<strong>發現程式有一個字串組合</strong></p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-04-20首發於<a href='https://www.zhienw.com/'>zhi旅程</a>，最後修改於2026-04-20</p>]]>
      </description>
      
        <category>picoctf</category>
      
    </item>
    
    

