</span></span></code></pre></div><p><img src="/images/Hidden_Cipher_2/2.webp" alt="image">
<strong>嘗試執行檔案</strong></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-SHELL" data-lang="SHELL"><span class="line"><span class="cl">./hiddencipher 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 回答問題</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p><img src="/images/Hidden_Cipher_2/3.webp" alt="image">
<strong>得到加密flag</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Encoded flag values:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-TEXT" data-lang="TEXT"><span class="line"><span class="cl">6720, 6300, 5940, 6660, 4020, 5040, 4200, 7380, 6120, 5820, 6420, 6060, 5700, 6120, 6480, 5820, 6180, 7500
</span></span></code></pre></div></blockquote>
<h2 id="使用-ida-進行靜態分析">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8-ida-%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c%e9%9d%9c%e6%85%8b%e5%88%86%e6%9e%90"></a>
使用 ida 進行靜態分析
</h2><p><strong>發現程式生成一個數學題目,列印並讀取使用者輸入</strong>
<img src="/images/Hidden_Cipher_2/4.webp" alt="image">
<strong>發現程式比對正確答案</strong>
<img src="/images/Hidden_Cipher_2/5.webp" alt="image">
<strong>發現程式去開啟讀入flag.txt內容</strong>
<img src="/images/Hidden_Cipher_2/6.webp" alt="image">
<strong>發限有一個encode_flag的函數,要對flag加密</strong>
<img src="/images/Hidden_Cipher_2/7.webp" alt="image">
<strong>發限有一個encode_flag的函數,用數學題答案對flag進行相乘加密</strong>
<img src="/images/Hidden_Cipher_2/8.webp" alt="image"></p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-04-18首發於<a href='https://www.zhienw.com/'>zhi旅程</a>，最後修改於2026-04-20</p>]]>
